WEBVTT

00:14:28.520 --> 00:14:31.336
Deep fun involves real vulnerability.

00:14:31.360 --> 00:14:35.976
You have intense interaction around
solving hard problems with high stakes.

00:14:36.000 --> 00:14:38.096
Like a team of lawyers,
trying to figure out

00:14:38.120 --> 00:14:40.976
how to present the best
closing argument in a case.

00:14:41.000 --> 00:14:43.960
Or a team of mechanics
trying to diagnose an engine failure.

00:14:44.800 --> 00:14:46.856
They might not say it's fun in the moment,

00:14:46.880 --> 00:14:50.376
but they often look back on the challenge
as a highlight of their job.

00:14:50.400 --> 00:14:54.016
DC: When you go inside a great culture,
they're not particularly bubbly.

00:14:54.040 --> 00:14:59.296
They are intense and there's a feeling
of togetherness, for sure,

00:14:59.320 --> 00:15:00.816
a deep feeling of togetherness.